{"tid":1977083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中国新加坡特區】又增623隻猴子！確診總數突破5000例","createTime":"2020-04-17T16:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T11:08:15.000Z","uid":293677,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"aba17e692209427030f59097105381ab260db97d","tid":1977083,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:33:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>又增623例！新加坡確診總數突破5000例</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n2020-04-17 19:48:29<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新加坡境內武漢肺炎（COVID-19）確診人數17日增加623例，累計確診總數突破5000例。</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n星國衛生部晚間在臉書發布訊息，今日新增623例確診，其中大多數是移工宿舍的外國工人，目前仍在研究這些病例的細節內容。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，新加坡至昨（16）日止，累計4427個確診病例，加上今天的新增確診數，總數已經來到5050例，而當中的10人已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡官方表示，當地最大感染群是S11榜鵝移工宿舍，至16日止累計979例，約佔該國總數的5分之1。官方今日尚未說明該宿舍的最新確診病例數目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3137443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3137443&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppepS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=0ebd774e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3137443&h=c9a838a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3137443</a><br />\n___________________________<br />\n<br />\n舊文節錄：<br />\n<br />\n＂陳振聲又提到香港目前出現的市民搶購糧食及廁紙的現象，認為是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「monkey see monkey do」（有樣學樣）</span></span>的「無腦行為」，「如果真的吃那麼多飯和即食麵，肯定腸胃炎」。他呼籲新加坡人不要讓自己變得那麼「醜怪」（disgraceful）， 不能學別人那樣「低能」（idiot）。＂<br />\n<br />\n新加坡部長揶揄香港「低能」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1977043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1977043</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">依家睇下邊個先係低能既monkey</span></span>"},{"pid":"25e0728c1ea9c961d2a73fc19b485afa0ea1d03e","tid":1977083,"uid":31475,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T01:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6Z2keb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6Z2keb.jpg&h=402ee677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Monkeypore<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9adf27e77389ff52cfba812365559374adb685ba","tid":1977083,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:05:53.000Z","msg":"過左疫情之後 想睇政府繼續奶共<br />\n班坡狗會有乜野反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef502a6a6963e28ff1727b0b07780d3a52f8b77","tid":1977083,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"Sick monkey everywhere"},{"pid":"a7b429aeaeda8a48ed32ed8f619b94bb925054c8","tid":1977083,"uid":268122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:08:00.000Z","msg":"希望台彎唔好賣米比佢<br />\n不過台仔錦大愛一定會賣"},{"pid":"c704eac8416a18af038b6446d04af9b24aa6a1c9","tid":1977083,"uid":31475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9adf27e77389ff52cfba812365559374adb685ba","tid":1977083,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:05:53.000Z","msg":"過左疫情之後 想睇政府繼續奶共<br />\n班坡狗會有乜野反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:05:19.000Z","msg":"Monkey坡自古以來就是中國一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af8796ed32feca0694a6cbf7ab367201f0348f7","tid":1977083,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"兩日就超過香港"},{"